"ນຄ້າ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font"
" class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການທຸກຊ່ອງທາງການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານໃນບ່ອນດຽວດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕ"
"ະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່"
"ານໂຊຊຽວມີເດຍ</font></strong>, ແລະ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະ"
"ຫຼາດຜ່ານ SMS</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage recurring tasks and never forget any replenishment or cleaning with "
"the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການວຽກທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນຊ້ຳໆ ແລະ ບໍ່ພາດການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ການເຮັດຄວາມສະອາດດ້ວຍ <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບໂຄງການ (Project)</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ງ່າຍກວ່າທີ່ເຄີຍດ້ວຍສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນຢ່າງສົມບູນ. (<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການບັນຊີ</font></strong>)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo also provides easy self ordering possibilities. Print a specific QR "
"code for each table on your Point of Sale settings and allow your customer "
"to order directly on their mobile phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຍັງມີຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ໃນການສັ່ງອາຫານດ້ວຍຕົນເອງທີ່ງ່າຍດາຍ. ພິມລະຫັດ QR ສະເພາະສຳລັບແຕ່ລະໂຕະໃນ"
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຈຸດຂາຍ ແລະ ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານສັ່ງອາຫານໂດຍກົງຜ່ານໂທລະສັບມືຖື."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" an additional cashier (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງເຂົ້າໃນແອັບຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດມັນເພື່ອປ່ຽນໂທລະສັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນເຄື່ອງຄິດເງິນເພີ່ມເຕີ"
"ມ (ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກ)."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as :"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ສິ້ນສຸດໃຫ້ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຊຸດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ ແລະ "
"ທົດລອງທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ເລີຍ!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"Receipt\" smart button to "
"validate your receipt and add these new products to your stock."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິນຄ້າມາຮອດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ໃບຮັບສິນຄ້າ\" ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນການຮັບ ແລະ ເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເຂົ້າ"
"ໃນສາງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_2
msgid "Online Payment"
msgstr "ການຊຳລະເງິນອອນໄລນ໌"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
